hing, or GPS to support our maritime supply chains.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Space-based technologies\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"New Zealand's security\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"wellbeing\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"satellite imagery\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"illegal fishing\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"our maritime supply chains\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Using space assets enables better communication, faster and better-informed decision making and helps New Zealand to maintain an effective, efficient, combat capable Defence Force.\\\"\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"space assets\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"better communication\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"faster and better-informed decision making\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"New Zealand\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"an effective, efficient, combat capable Defence Force\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand is already a member of the Combined Space Operations initiative, which is a forum aimed at building norms of behaviour in space and removing barriers to multinational military space cooperation amongst like-minded nations.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"New Zealand\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"the Combined Space Operations initiative\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"a forum\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"norms\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"behaviour\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"barriers\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1673}, {